446
00:40:28,786 --> 00:40:29,932
Police!

447
00:40:31,228 --> 00:40:34,001
Step out of the vehicle
with your hands up.

448
00:40:48,905 --> 00:40:51,301
- We got to move.
- I can't.

449
00:40:55,137 --> 00:40:56,451
Oh, my God.

450
00:41:05,568 --> 00:41:06,590
I failed him.

